## About Elizabeth Ashley

Elizabeth Ashley is a globally recognised educator in clinical aromatherapy, UK Director for NAHA, and author of *The Secret Healer Aromatherapy Manuals*. Her work focuses on restoring traditional aromatherapy knowledge and providing clear, trustworthy education for modern essential oil users.

